# Complex Numbers

> Standard library base complex number math functions.

<section class="usage">

## Usage

``` javascript
var ns = require( '@stdlib/math/base/complex' );
```

#### ns

Standard library base complex number math functions.

``` javascript
var o = ns;
// returns {...}
```
